           SHORT="Junction Typeface"
cat << EOF
Inspired by my favorite humanist sans serif typefaces, such as Meta, Myriad, and
Scala, Junction is where the best qualities of serif and sans serif typefaces
come together. It has the hand drawn and human qualities of a serif, and still
retains the clarity and efficiencies of a sans serif typeface. It combines the
best of both worlds.
EOF
